msgid "Running DeepSeek-V3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../references/amd.md:108
msgid ""
"The only difference when running DeepSeek-V3 is in how you start the server. "
"Here's an example command:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../references/amd.md:110
msgid ""
"drun -p 30000:30000 \\\n"
